WEBVTT

00:08:27.967 --> 00:08:30.071
I know you can make
a long list of countries

00:08:30.095 --> 00:08:33.218
that are not really stepping up,

00:08:33.242 --> 00:08:35.690
but I'm more interested
in the other part --

00:08:35.714 --> 00:08:37.904
is there somebody
who's doing the right thing?

00:08:38.402 --> 00:08:40.833
AG: Well, 86 percent
of the refugees in the world

00:08:40.857 --> 00:08:42.912
are in the developing world.

00:08:42.936 --> 00:08:46.256
And if you look at
countries like Ethiopia --

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:50.057
Ethiopia has received
more than 600,000 refugees.

00:08:50.486 --> 00:08:52.502
All the borders in Ethiopia are open.

00:08:53.304 --> 00:08:55.172
And they have, as a policy,

00:08:55.196 --> 00:08:59.292
they call the "people to people" policy
that every refugee should be received.

